## Where to Place Action Items

**CRITICAL RULE:** Action items belong ONLY in `/active_leads/` and `/projects/` files.

**‚ùå NEVER place action items in `/people/` files.** People files document relationships and interactions, not tasks.

### In Project Files
Place under `## Action Items` section after status and overview:

```markdown
## Status
- **Current Status:** In Progress
- **Next Milestone:** Complete Phase 1
- **Last Updated:** 2025-11-13

## Overview
[project details]

## Action Items
- [ ] **URGENT:** Finalize proposal document
- [ ] Review technical specifications
- [ ] Schedule kickoff meeting
```

### In Lead Files
Place under `## Action Items` section after status and meeting notes:

```markdown
## Status
- **Stage:** Proposal Sent
- **Next Step:** Follow up on proposal
- **Last Updated:** 2025-11-13

## Action Items
- [ ] Follow up in 3 days if no response
- [ ] Prepare pricing alternatives
```

### In Task Context Files
Place under `## Completion Criteria` as deliverables:

```markdown
## Completion Criteria
- [ ] Deliverable 1 *(added 2025-11-13, from update 2025-11-13)*
- [ ] Deliverable 2 *(added 2025-11-13, from update 2025-11-13)*
```

