## Script Integration

The `action_items_report.py` script extracts these automatically:

```bash
# Show all action items across CRM
python3 scripts/action_items_report.py

# Show only urgent items
python3 scripts/action_items_report.py --priority URGENT

# Export as markdown
python3 scripts/action_items_report.py --format markdown --output action_items.md
```

The script automatically:
- Detects priority from keywords and emojis
- Extracts dates from `*(added YYYY-MM-DD)*` tags
- Finds context from section headers
- Sorts by priority and date
- Outputs with full file paths for easy navigation

